  "answer": "**Meherbaan ho ke bula lo mujhe chaaho jis waqt**  \n**Main gaya waqt nahin hoon ke phir aa bhi na sakoon**[^1]\n\n[^1]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, ch. 135 (\"Meherbaan ho ke bula lo mujhe chaaho jis waqt\"), [/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/135-meherbaan-ho-ke-bula-lo-mujhe-chaaho-jis-waqt/transliteration/](https://falsafa.corpus/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/135-meherbaan-ho-ke-bula-lo-mujhe-chaaho-jis-waqt/transliteration/) (transliteration; matlaʹ, or opening couplet, from the ghazal's first verse paragraph).[^2]\n\n[^2]: English translation: \"Be kind, and call me to you when you please; I am not bygone time, that I cannot return with ease.\"[/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/135-meherbaan-ho-ke-bula-lo-mujhe-chaaho-jis-waqt/translation/#p-274a7b](https://falsafa.corpus/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/135-meherbaan-ho-ke-bula-lo-mujhe-chaaho-jis-waqt/translation/#p-274a7b).",
